"""sxy estimate from ROI cross-sectional area distribution.

Per-cell xy bounding-box area (proxy for max xy cross-section):
  CZ: from segmentation_masks.tif (regionprops)
  HCR: from hcr_gfp_df.global_bbox (already computed, GFP+ only);
       strict BIC-GMM threshold applied on density.

Filters:
  CZ: all cells with depth in [d_skin, cz_99pct_depth]
  HCR: BIC-strict GFP+ within HCR center 1/4 FOV, depth ≥ d_skin

Scale ratio (linear stretch sxy under tissue expansion):
  area_HCR = sxy^2 · area_CZ  →  sxy = sqrt(median(area_HCR)/median(area_CZ))

Also produces area-vs-depth diagnostic plots.

Spot subjects only (have global_bbox): 788406, 790322, 767018, 782149.
Intensity subjects (755252, 767022) lack per-cell bbox in hcr_gfp_df.
"""
